gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 128, Thunder 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Thunder, 128-95. Nikola Jokic led all scorers with 28 points (12-16 FG), 14 rebounds, and five assists in 30 minutes played for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 19 points and eight assists in the victory. Chet Holmgren tallied a career-high 19 points for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 3-0 on the season, while the Thunder fall to 2-1.
